Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.91,1:20:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole picture, karmically, the best thing you can do right now is get wiped out, why,\Noh, you've forgotten all the tens of thousands you slaughtered mercilessly, outside of this
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.44,1:20:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,bodiness, oh, yeah, right, you denied mercy to the innocent, and now you know, you're not\Ngoing to know what it's like, to feel blown up, the world is not in love, so, it is the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.95,1:21:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,this world is the ultimate for our spiritual growth and development, the karmic opportunities\Nof a human lifetime are staggering, you can undo negative karma at one point, and be earning
